We are making an autobattler game. This is a single player game.

The player has 5 characters. On the players turn they all atack one by one.

They have stats, modifiers, and abilities, abilities take in a contextType, this should be a large zod descriminated union.

Modifiers can attack on the start of a turn, when hit by an ability with a certain context type, on Damage, on Heal. There are also permant modifiers that just effect things statically.

Characters have base stats and a list of modifiers.

All rules are applied by the central game-engine.svelte.

